text: is the third studio album by Miyavi. It was released on June 1, 2005. Its limited edition comes with the song "Shakespeare ni Sasagu" (シェイクスピアに捧ぐ) instead of tracks eleven and twelve. It charted 10th on Oricon. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2005 albums Category:Miyavi albums Category:Free-Will albums sv:Miyavizm
